preference.name: TCAA113_DWFX_by_publish_layout_nums
preference.preference_description: List of indexes of layouts to be published in DWFx auxiliary files. This option is taken into consideration only if TCAA113_DWFX_generation_mode is set to 1 and TCAA113_DWFX_by_publish_select_mode is set to 2. Possible values: Integer indexes from 1 to N, where N is the maximum number of layouts. Value 0 can be used to identify the model space. Default value is 1.
